data.description: This like-new 2020 home has 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and offers 1,747 square feet of modern living space. Featuring a large, fully fenced yard, this property will be great for entertaining or adding a pool. Inside, you'll find an open-concept design and luxurious owner's suite. Located in a peaceful Southwest Cape Coral neighborhood, this property has easy access to restaurants, shopping, and downtown. It's the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours!
